        module</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " otherprops="examples" xtrc="p:7;87:32" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/relax-ng-coding-constraint-modules.dita">The following code fragment illustrates the domains contribution for
        a constraint module <ph class="- topic/ph " xtrc="ph:4;88:34" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/relax-ng-coding-constraint-modules.dita">that restricts the task requirements
          domain:</ph><codeblock class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xml:space="preserve" xtrc="codeblock:4;89:34" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/relax-ng-coding-constraint-modules.dita">&lt;moduleDesc&gt;
